cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.AI

The paper discusses the issue of security in Mobile Ad hoc Networks (MANETs), which is a subfield of computer networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper proposes a new Intrusion Detection System (IDS) algorithm, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The algorithm involves identifying and blocking misbehaving nodes, which can be considered as a form of data analysis (cs.DS) and system optimization (cs.SY). Additionally, the proposed algorithm involves machine learning techniques to identify selfish nodes, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
